<h1>Password Reset</h1>
<a
    style="
        background-color: #219ebc;
        font-size: 1rem;
        padding: 0.375rem 0.75rem;
        border: 1px solid transparent;
        border-color: #219ebc;
        border-radius: 0.25rem;
        cursor: pointer;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: black;
    "
    href="<%= passwordResetURL %>"
>
    Reset Your Password
</a>
<h3>Click the button above to reset your password.</h3>
<p>This password reset will expire in 10 minutes.</p>
<p>
    If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email.
</p>
<p>If the button above does not work you can copy and paste this url.</p>
<p><%= passwordResetURL %></p>
